{"article_id":"w3ZNKvCvdpDbIYgo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Mexican President Enrique Peña Nieto on Thursday canceled a meeting with US President Donald Trump","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that had been set for next week","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"after renewed tensions erupted over Trump 's plan","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"to build a wall on the border .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"`` This morning we have informed the White House","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that I will not attend the meeting","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"scheduled for next Tuesday with the POTUS , ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Peña Nieto tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Earlier Thursday morning , Trump had tweeted","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that it would be better to skip the meeting","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"if Peña Nieto continued to insist","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Mexico would not pay for the wall","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"-- something the Mexican leader had said as recently as Wednesday evening .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"`` If Mexico is unwilling to pay for the badly needed wall ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"then it would be better to cancel the upcoming meeting , ''","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"Trump tweeted","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and in an earlier tweet he noted the US 's trade deficit with Mexico and what he said","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"were the American job losses","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"caused by NAFTA .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"The U.S. has a 60 billion dollar trade deficit with Mexico .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"It has been a one-sided deal from the beginning of NAFTA with massive numbers ... of jobs and companies lost .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"If Mexico is unwilling to pay for the badly needed wall ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"then it would be better to cancel the upcoming meeting .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Trump spoke about the cancellation during remarks at a gathering of congressional Republicans in Philadelphia .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that he and the Mexican president had mutually agreed to scrap their planned get together ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and he repeated his position","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that the US wo n't fund the wall .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` Unless Mexico will treat the US fairly , with respect ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"such a meeting is fruitless ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and I want to go a different route , ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Trump told House and Senate GOP lawmakers .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` I have no choice . '","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"' `` Border security is a serious , serious issue and a national problem , ''","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"`` Most illegal immigration is coming from our Southern border . ''","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"On Wednesday night , Peña Nieto had said at that time","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"he did not see a need","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to scrap the get together","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"-- but he strongly reiterated","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that his country would n't fund any border wall ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Senate Majority leader Mitch McConnell said Thursday","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"would cost $ 12- $ 15 billion","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"`` President Trump 's insistence","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that Mexico will pay for the wall","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"has once again just been proven as delusional fiction by the Mexican President , ''","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"said House Democratic leader Nancy Pelosi .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"`` The wall is a multi-billion dollar boondoggle in the making ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"and Republicans should be embarrassed about their brazen hypocrisy","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"in enabling it . ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` Mexico does not believe in walls .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"I 've said time again ;","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Mexico will not pay for any wall , ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"the Mexican president said in a video statement","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"posted to Twitter","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"and translated by CNN from Spanish .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"The back-and-forth between the two leaders began last year during the first days of the Trump campaign","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"when he called","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"some Mexicans","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"entering the US","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"criminals and rapists","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and tensions lingered throughout the 2016 contest .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"They escalated sharply over the last 24 hours","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"when Trump took executive action on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to begin the process","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"of erecting a wall .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The President announced that move","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"while a high-level Mexican delegation was visiting the White House","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"-- the first foreign representatives","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to come","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"since Trump took office --","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"for meetings with top officials ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"including Chief of Staff Reince Priebus and adviser Jared Kushner .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"One member of the delegation , Mexican Foreign Minister Luis Videgaray ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"who had led talks between his government and the Trump transition team ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"was in his car on his way to meetings at the Department of Homeland Security on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"when he suddenly decided","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"he would not attend .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"`` We will work to schedule a future meeting","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and will continue to keep the lines of communication and partnership open , ''","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"said DHS Spokeswoman Gillian Christensen .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"Trump signs executive actions on border wall","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Trump signs executive actions on border wall","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"02:40","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"In his video address , Peña Nieto also said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"he had ordered government agencies to step up protection for immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"`` I 've asked for the minister of Foreign Relations to re-enforce protection measures to our citizens , ''","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that the 50 Mexican consulates in the US will be used","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to defend the rights of immigrants in the country","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"and issued a call to action to legislators and civic organizations","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to help immigrants .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Peña Nieto closed his message","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"by saying","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Mexico offers and expects respect .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"`` Mexico offers its friendship to the people of the United States","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"and expresses its wish","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"to arrive at agreements with its government , deals","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that will be in favor of Mexico and the Mexicans , ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Earlier Wednesday , Trump signed two executive orders","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"directing construction of a wall on the US-Mexico border ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"boosting border patrol forces ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"and increasing the number of immigration enforcement officers","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"who carry out deportations .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Meanwhile , the Mexican officials","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who arrived Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"had been expected to lay the groundwork for Peña Nieto 's visit next week ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"which Mexican diplomats had seen as an important opportunity","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"to try to move past the anti-Mexico rhetoric","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Trump used during the campaign","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and a chance","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"to put the relationship back on track .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` There is ... frustration with our government and ourselves","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that we have not been able to tell the story of this important relationship , ''","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"a Mexican diplomat told CNN ahead of the delegation 's visit .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"`` There are a lot of stereotypes of Mexicans in the US ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"but there are also stereotypes of Americans in Mexico .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"It is in the interest of both governments to explain what this relationship is","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"and what we can do together . ''","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"In a Monday speech , Peña Nieto said","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"his government is prepared to negotiate with the US","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"if Mexico 's national sovereignty is respected .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"He laid out economic integration and respect for the rights of migrants and the money","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"they send home","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"as his nation 's key negotiating points .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"`` Neither confrontation nor submission .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Dialogue is the solution , ''","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Peña Nieto said .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Trump has suggested","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"some of the $ 25 billion in annual remittances","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"that migrants return home","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"would be retained","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"to pay for the border wall .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":3},{"id":141,"text":"Trump :","depth":4},{"id":142,"text":"Mexico to reimburse US for wall","depth":4},{"id":143,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":4},{"id":144,"text":"MUST WATCH Trump :","depth":6},{"id":145,"text":"Mexico to reimburse US for wall","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"02:54","depth":5},{"id":147,"text":"Trump flew to Mexico City during his campaign","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"to meet Peña Nieto","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"they discussed a wall","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"Trump has vowed to build on the US southern border ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"but not his demand","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"that Mexico pay for it","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"-- an assertion the Mexican president later disputed .","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"`` At the start of the conversation with Donald Trump , I made it clear","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"that Mexico will not pay for the wall , ''","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"Peña Nieto tweeted ,","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"after their meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"which was widely viewed as a public relations disaster for Peña Nieto .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":319,"left":299,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":242,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":217,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":183,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":168,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":164,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":0,"right":1